{"type":"message","id":"20706005","parentId":"6b218ec4","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:59:55.230Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8vt9ys602cr6_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"tiktok-shop-growth  TikTok Shop Growth\nSummary: Provides TikTok Shop ecommerce teams with tailored content strategies and weekly plans to boost sales through focused video ideas and commerce-driven content...\nOwner: leooooooow\nCreated: 2026-03-19T11:22:04.068Z\nUpdated: 2026-05-11T09:33:53.442Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nLicense: MIT-0 (Free to use, modify, and redistribute. No attribution required.)\nTags: latest=1.0.0\nSelected: 1.0.0\nSelected At: 2026-03-19T11:22:04.068Z\nChangelog: TikTok Shop-focused ecommerce content strategy skill\nSecurity: CLEAN\nChecked: 2026-05-19T07:45:50.789Z\nModel: gpt-5.5\nFiles:\nSKILL.md  3.5KB  eae3f0ec08c0e8afc0fa47a8df6386cc4897536d5478279f37fd5abf9244b536  text/markdown\nreferences/output-template.md  320B  fd84fb34ab179578552af419b4f01247a8f1bd3a349495e3803148eed84fd680  text/markdown"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2881,"aggregated":"tiktok-shop-growth  TikTok Shop Growth\nSummary: Provides TikTok Shop ecommerce teams with tailored content strategies and weekly plans to boost sales through focused video ideas and commerce-driven content...\nOwner: leooooooow\nCreated: 2026-03-19T11:22:04.068Z\nUpdated: 2026-05-11T09:33:53.442Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nLicense: MIT-0 (Free to use, modify, and redistribute. No attribution required.)\nTags: latest=1.0.0\nSelected: 1.0.0\nSelected At: 2026-03-19T11:22:04.068Z\nChangelog: TikTok Shop-focused ecommerce content strategy skill\nSecurity: CLEAN\nChecked: 2026-05-19T07:45:50.789Z\nModel: gpt-5.5\nFiles:\nSKILL.md  3.5KB  eae3f0ec08c0e8afc0fa47a8df6386cc4897536d5478279f37fd5abf9244b536  text/markdown\nreferences/output-template.md  320B  fd84fb34ab179578552af419b4f01247a8f1bd3a349495e3803148eed84fd680  text/markdown","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"