{"type":"message","id":"321a496b","parentId":"20706005","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:59:59.880Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me also get the SKILL.md for tiktok-shop-growth\n","thinkingSignature":"093c48dee96387ed7174e549bf270b052566c5c3b00e3c8703d0aa43eb6431d8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7pjwmxm23r9v_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub inspect tiktok-shop-growth --file SKILL.md 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3880,"output":55,"cacheRead":71917,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75852,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779955195389,"responseId":"066728fb4ba64bf3dd8d2370447511c6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"890b32bf","parentId":"321a496b","timestamp":"2026-05-28T08:00:06.411Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7pjwmxm23r9v_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TikTok Growth\n\nHelp ecommerce teams, TikTok Shop operators, and creators decide what to post on TikTok to improve the odds of generating traction, clicks, and sales.\n\nUse this skill when a user wants practical TikTok content guidance tied to commerce outcomes rather than vague “growth hacks.” This skill is best for product-led short-form planning, creator content direction, TikTok Shop content systems, and weekly content planning for brands or affiliates.\n\n## Problem it solves\nMany teams know they “should post more on TikTok” but do not know what kinds of videos are actually worth making. They jump between trends, hooks, and formats without a coherent content system. This skill turns product, audience, and account context into content pillars, video angle ideas, and testing priorities.\n\n## What this skill is for\nThis is not a generic TikTok growth encyclopedia.\nIt is a TikTok Shop and ecommerce-oriented content strategy skill that helps answer questions like:\n- What should we post this week?\n- Which content angles are more likely to drive sales?\n- What kinds of videos should this product or creator test first?\n- How should we balance reach content vs. conversion content?\n\n## Use when\n- A brand or creator asks what to post on TikTok\n- A TikTok Shop team needs content direction tied to sales outcomes\n- The user wants a weekly posting plan, testing matrix, or content pillars\n- A product has potential but the team lacks clear content angles\n- A creator account feels random and needs structure\n\n## Do not use when\n- The task is real-time trend scraping or news monitoring\n- The user wants automated TikTok posting or browser automation\n- The user needs deep analytics from a specific video rather than content planning\n- The user needs fully written scripts only, without strategy context\n\n## Inputs to ask for\n- Product, category, and price point\n- Target audience and buyer awareness level\n- TikTok Shop status or creator/account type\n- Current content situation: what has worked, failed, or felt repetitive\n- Main goal: reach, engagement, clicks, conversions, creator recruiting, etc.\n- Offer, differentiators, and objections\n- Available assets: demos, testimonials, creators, reviews, product visuals\n\n## Workflow\n1. Clarify the product, buyer, account type, and business goal\n2. Identify the most likely purchase triggers, objections, and curiosity hooks\n3. Build 3-5 content pillars tied to actual commerce outcomes\n4. Suggest video types and recurring formats for each pillar\n5. Separate top-of-funnel reach ideas from conversion-oriented ideas\n6. Rank testing priorities so the user knows what to make first\n7. Convert strategy into a short weekly or batch content plan\n\n## Output requirements\nReturn:\n1. 3-5 content pillars\n2. Best content angles by pillar\n3. Suggested TikTok video types or series formats\n4. Hook directions to test\n5. Reach vs. conversion balance recommendation\n6. Weekly post plan or priority matrix\n7. Optional watchouts: what not to overdo or test too early\n\n## Quality standards\n- Advice must feel specific to TikTok Shop / ecommerce, not generic social media advice\n- Recommendations should connect content to likely business outcomes\n- Output should be practical enough for a creator or operator to use immediately\n- Avoid fake certainty, generic trend talk, or overpromising “viral” results\n- Keep language concrete, creator-native, and commercially useful\n\n## Example prompts\n- What should we post on TikTok Shop for this product?\n- Give me a TikTok content plan that is more likely to drive sales\n- Our TikTok content feels random. Build a better content system"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6419,"aggregated":"# TikTok Growth\n\nHelp ecommerce teams, TikTok Shop operators, and creators decide what to post on TikTok to improve the odds of generating traction, clicks, and sales.\n\nUse this skill when a user wants practical TikTok content guidance tied to commerce outcomes rather than vague “growth hacks.” This skill is best for product-led short-form planning, creator content direction, TikTok Shop content systems, and weekly content planning for brands or affiliates.\n\n## Problem it solves\nMany teams know they “should post more on TikTok” but do not know what kinds of videos are actually worth making. They jump between trends, hooks, and formats without a coherent content system. This skill turns product, audience, and account context into content pillars, video angle ideas, and testing priorities.\n\n## What this skill is for\nThis is not a generic TikTok growth encyclopedia.\nIt is a TikTok Shop and ecommerce-oriented content strategy skill that helps answer questions like:\n- What should we post this week?\n- Which content angles are more likely to drive sales?\n- What kinds of videos should this product or creator test first?\n- How should we balance reach content vs. conversion content?\n\n## Use when\n- A brand or creator asks what to post on TikTok\n- A TikTok Shop team needs content direction tied to sales outcomes\n- The user wants a weekly posting plan, testing matrix, or content pillars\n- A product has potential but the team lacks clear content angles\n- A creator account feels random and needs structure\n\n## Do not use when\n- The task is real-time trend scraping or news monitoring\n- The user wants automated TikTok posting or browser automation\n- The user needs deep analytics from a specific video rather than content planning\n- The user needs fully written scripts only, without strategy context\n\n## Inputs to ask for\n- Product, category, and price point\n- Target audience and buyer awareness level\n- TikTok Shop status or creator/account type\n- Current content situation: what has worked, failed, or felt repetitive\n- Main goal: reach, engagement, clicks, conversions, creator recruiting, etc.\n- Offer, differentiators, and objections\n- Available assets: demos, testimonials, creators, reviews, product visuals\n\n## Workflow\n1. Clarify the product, buyer, account type, and business goal\n2. Identify the most likely purchase triggers, objections, and curiosity hooks\n3. Build 3-5 content pillars tied to actual commerce outcomes\n4. Suggest video types and recurring formats for each pillar\n5. Separate top-of-funnel reach ideas from conversion-oriented ideas\n6. Rank testing priorities so the user knows what to make first\n7. Convert strategy into a short weekly or batch content plan\n\n## Output requirements\nReturn:\n1. 3-5 content pillars\n2. Best content angles by pillar\n3. Suggested TikTok video types or series formats\n4. Hook directions to test\n5. Reach vs. conversion balance recommendation\n6. Weekly post plan or priority matrix\n7. Optional watchouts: what not to overdo or test too early\n\n## Quality standards\n- Advice must feel specific to TikTok Shop / ecommerce, not generic social media advice\n- Recommendations should connect content to likely business outcomes\n- Output should be practical enough for a creator or operator to use immediately\n- Avoid fake certainty, generic trend talk, or overpromising “viral” results\n- Keep language concrete, creator-native, and commercially useful\n\n## Example prompts\n- What should we post on TikTok Shop for this product?\n- Give me a TikTok content plan that is more likely to drive sales\n- Our TikTok content feels random. Build a better content system","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779955206407}}
{"type":"message","id":"297e1359","parentId":"890b32bf","timestamp":"2026-05-28T08:00:48.299Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have comprehensive information on all the key skills. Let me compile the information for the user in a clear format with URLs/references where available.\n\nThe key skills and their details:\n\n1. **tiktok-shop-automation** - TikTok Shop Automation\n   - Owner: lvjunjie-byte\n   - Security: SUSPICIOUS (this is a warning flag)\n   - Requires: TIKTOK_SHOP_API_KEY, TIKTOK_SHOP_API_SECRET, TIKTOK_SHOP_SELLER_ID\n   - Has CLI commands and API integration\n   - Need TikTok Shop Seller Center API access\n   \n2. **tiktok-shop-analytics** - TikTok Shop Analytics\n   - Owner: nexscope (nexscope.ai)\n   - Security: CLEAN\n   - Install: npx skills add nexscope/tiktok-shop-analytics\n   - No external API needed apparently\n   \n3. **ecommerce-product-research** - Ecommerce Product Research via PipiAds\n   - Owner: fanyanggod\n   - Security: CLEAN\n   - Requires: PIPIADS_API_KEY (from pipiads.com/pipispy.com)\n   - Uses MCP server: pipiads-mcp-server@1.0.3\n   \n4. **tiktok-shop-growth** - TikTok Shop Growth Content Strategy\n   - Owner: leooooooow\n   - Security: CLEAN\n   - No external API needed\n   \n5. **tiktok-ads** - TikTok Ads Strategy & Best Practices\n   - Owner: ivangdavila\n   - Security: CLEAN\n   - No external API needed - just knowledge/strategy guidance\n   \n6. **ecommerce-video-ai** - Ecommerce Video AI\n   - Owner: imwyvern\n   - Security: CLEAN\n   - References: mediaclawbot.com for batch video production\n\nThe user wanted to see the links/references for these skills, so I need to provide those along with what each skill requires to function.\n","thinkingSignature":"c1c3f4075bf8e553085263daacb0897a64b6d9e97681668ac013323de4d07638"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的，我来看一下这些 Skill 的具体信息，包括是否需要 API、依赖什么、是否有安全警告等：\n\n---\n\n## 📦 推荐的 TikTok Shop Skills 详情\n\n### 1️⃣ **tiktok-shop-automation** — TikTok Shop 自动化 ⚠️ 有安全警告\n\n| 项目 | 详情 |\n|------|------|\n| **作者** | lvjunjie-byte |\n| **安全** | 🔴 **SUSPICIOUS** |\n| **License** | MIT-0 |\n| **功能** | 商品管理、订单处理、数据分析、营销自动化、CLI 命令行工具 |\n| **依赖** | TikTok Shop Seller Center API（需要申请） |\n| **环境变量** | `TIKTOK_SHOP_API_KEY`, `TIKTOK_SHOP_API_SECRET`, `TIKTOK_SHOP_SELLER_ID` |\n| **获取 API** | TikTok Shop Seller Center → 我的账号 → API 应用 |\n| **费用** | 免费（但需要自行有 TikTok Shop 卖家账号和 API 权限） |\n| **文件** | CLI 工具 + API SDK + 飞书集成模块 |\n\n**风险提示**：这个 Skill 被标记为 SUSPICIOUS（可疑），安装前建议先 review 源码，或等作者更新修复后再装。\n\n---\n\n### 2️⃣ **tiktok-shop-analytics** — TikTok Shop 数据分析 ✅ 干净\n\n| 项目 | 详情 |\n|------|------|\n| **作者** | nexscope（[nexscope.ai](https://www.nexscope.ai)） |\n| **安全** | ✅ CLEAN |\n| **License** | MIT-0 |\n| **功能** | 销售分析、视频/直播表现、创作者 ROI、广告效率、产品趋势、客户画像 |\n| **依赖** | **无需外部 API**，纯分析能力 |\n| **安装** | `npx skills add nexscope/tiktok-shop-analytics` |\n\n**使用场景**：\n- \"分析我的 TikTok Shop 表现，找出增长机会\"\n- \"哪些产品卖得最好？为什么？\"\n- \"追踪创作者联盟活动的 ROI\"\n\n---\n\n### 3️⃣ **ecommerce-product-research** — 选品研究 via PipiAds\n\n| 项目 | 详情 |\n|------|------|\n| **作者** | fanyanggod |\n| **安全** | ✅ CLEAN |\n| **License** | MIT-0 |\n| **功能** | TikTok/Facebook 广告数据、产品研究、店铺分析（基于 PipiAds） |\n| **依赖** | 🔑 **PIPIADS_API_KEY** |\n| **获取 API** | [pipiads.com](https://pipiads.com)（看数据）+ [pipispy.com](https://www.pipispy.com)（API 密钥） |\n| **MCP Server** | `pipiads-mcp-server@1.0.3`（需要 npm 安装） |\n| **费用** | PipiAds 付费服务（按 API 调用扣积分） |\n\n**核心工具**：\n- `search_ads` / `search_products` — 搜索广告和产品\n- `get_ad_detail` — 广告详情\n- `get_store_detail` — 店铺详情\n- `get_store_data_analysis` — 店铺数据分析\n\n---\n\n### 4️⃣ **tiktok-shop-growth** — TikTok Shop 内容增长策略 ✅ 干净\n\n| 项目 | 详情 |\n|------|------|\n| **作者** | leooooooow |\n| **安全** | ✅ CLEAN |\n| **License** | MIT-0 |\n| **功能** | 内容策略、周计划、视频创意、产品推广角度 |\n| **依赖** | **无需外部 API**，纯策略规划 |\n| **输出** | 3-5 个内容支柱、视频角度建议、周计划、测试优先级 |\n\n**使用场景**：\n- \"我们应该发什么 TikTok 内容来提升销售？\"\n- \"给我一个能带货的 TikTok 内容计划\"\n- \"我们的 TikTok 内容太乱了，帮我构建一个系统\"\n\n---\n\n### 5️⃣ **tiktok-ads** — TikTok 广告投放策略 ✅ 干净\n\n| 项目 | 详情 |\n|------|------|\n| **作者** | ivangdavila |\n| **安全** | ✅ CLEAN |\n| **License** | MIT-0 |\n| **功能** | 广告策略、创意最佳实践、Spark Ads、投放优化 |\n| **依赖** | **无需外部 API**，纯知识/策略指导 |\n| **覆盖** | 投放技巧、竞价策略、流量机制、创意思维、归因追踪 |\n\n**核心知识点**：\n- Spark Ads 运作方式\n- 投放目标和竞价策略选择\n- 创意测试方法论\n- 归因和转化追踪\n\n---\n\n### 6️⃣ **ecommerce-video-ai** — 电商视频 AI ✅ 干净\n\n| 项目 | 详情 |\n|------|------|\n| **作者** | imwyvern |\n| **安全** | ✅ CLEAN |\n| **License** | MIT-0 |\n| **功能** | 产品图转视频、listing 转脚本、演示视频、对比视频 |\n| **依赖** | **无需外部 API**（本地处理） |\n| **付费升级** | [mediaclawbot.com](https://mediaclawbot.com)（批量生产） |\n\n**输出格式**：\n- 15-30s 产品展示视频\n- 9:16 社交广告\n- 功能演示（3-5s 每个）\n- UGC 风格口碑视频\n- 季促/大促视频\n\n---\n\n## 📋 安装优先级建议\n\n| 优先级 | Skill | 原因 | API 需要 |\n|--------|-------|------|----------|\n| **P0** | tiktok-shop-analytics | 数据分析是核心需求，立即可用 | 无 |\n| **P0** | tiktok-shop-growth | 内容策略，立即可用 | 无 |\n| **P0** | tiktok-ads | 投流知识储备，立即可用 | 无 |\n| **P1** | ecommerce-product-research | 选品数据支撑 | 需要 PipiAds |\n| **P1** | ecommerce-video-ai | 视频内容制作 | 无 |\n| **⚠️ P2** | tiktok-shop-automation | 功能最全但有安全警告 | 需要 TikTok API |\n\n---\n\n你想先装哪几个？我可以帮你执行安装。需要你提供的主要是 **PipiADS 的 API Key**（如果装选品那个），其他的可以直接装。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4340,"output":1765,"cacheRead":72265,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78370,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779955206641,"responseId":"06672907e66247a8c3fc42a019c59e41"}}
